com.software.reuze

Class d_MapAustraliaRoadsSimplified

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.software.reuze.d_MapExtendable
      • com.software.reuze.d_MapAustraliaRoadsSimplified
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    d_i_Map

    public class d_MapAustraliaRoadsSimplified
extends d_MapExtendable
    Represents a simplified road map of Australia. The initialization method is declared static. So it can also be used to initialize other specialized subclasses of d_MapExtendable with road map data from Australia. The data was extracted from a class developed by Felix Knittel.
    Author:
    Ruediger Lunde
